commit_list.message:
refs #73

Removed timeouts,small margin fix

In order to remove the timeouts I have used evalAsync . After some searching  I realised that the graphs didn't draw  because of the DOM objects, which were not created on time . Queueing the graph function with evalAsync made sure that the objects were created and ready to use.

dashboard.js:
    >Enclosed all draw graph timeouts in $evalAsync
graphs.js:
    >Added 5 pixels on line graph margins so the date text won't go off widget
